# All profile: Complete set of all available configuration variables
#
# This profile installs every variable from .env-templates/ to .env/default/
# Useful for development, testing, or when you want full control over all settings.
#
# IMPORTANT NOTES:
# - Uses arity-specific interpreters (wireguard_add1/2/3) instead of family-level
#   interpreter (wireguard_add) to avoid heterogeneous family issues
# - See docs/ARCHITECTURE.md "DANGER: Heterogeneous Family Commands" for details
#
# To regenerate this list after adding new variables:
#   cd template/environment
#   ls -1 | grep -v '^VPN_SWITCH_PROFILE_' | tr '\n' ' '
#   # Then manually replace heterogeneous family interpreters with arity-specific ones
#
# To create a custom profile based on this:
#   cat VPN_SWITCH_PROFILE_ALL > VPN_SWITCH_PROFILE_PRODUCTION
#   # Then edit to remove unwanted variables
